Shadow of cloaked vessel 
 
If you zoom in on Google Earth on the Western side of Cyprus (35˚08 N 32˚39 E) you will see a shadow. It may look as the shadow of a mountain’s crest, but if you look closer, you can see it is not. The sun is too high on the sky for the mountain to cast this specific shadow, which look like a Stealth bomber. Also similar shadows would be seen on other northwalls in the area, but there are none. 
 
If it is a glitch in Google Earth cameras, then I expect these to be found elsewhere, but I have not been able to locate any. 
 
I think it may be the shadow of a craft - terrestrial or not - with advanced cloaking capability. If a Google airplane shot photos from above, the craft would not be seen - only its shadow.

On the evening these events took place, I had just arrived at my mother's house off Hwy. 78 in a little subdivision close to and across the highway from Berlin G. Myers Lumber Co. 
 
 Not long after arriving I heard people talking loudly and with excitement just outside of the house. 
 
When I went to the door there were about 15 or 20 neighbors looking and pointing at something in the sky above the subdivision. 
 
I went onto the porch to investigate and sure enough there was some sort of craft hovering slowly high in the sky as if it was looking for something. 
 
I ran in the house to get my driving glasses and when I returned the craft was so low  I swear you wanted to reach up to try to touch it. It was huge and ominous looking. 
 
It was shaped like your everyday 'Flying Saucer' medium colored gray flat metal construction. 
 
As it continued to silently hover over our heads, a relatively small compartment slowly descended from the middle of bottom of the craft... there were lights in it but I couldn't see any occupants. Everyone was spellbound and silent. 
 
All of a sudden and without warning it disappeared in an instant....and immediately a military looking helecopter came swooping in so close & fast over our houses, we ducked in panic. The chopper circled the area quickly once and headed off toward the airforce base. 
 
Personally I'm not prone to believe in a future allien invasion...we have enough acting like that down here already, but I know what we all saw and quiet honestly I'm glad I am able to share the experience even though it has been about 50 years ago. God bless and keep looking up!!!

I saw an alien that didnt seem intelligent go to a ship and then fly away. 
 
This happened back in 2012, and no one has ever believed me then I found this website. 
 
It was early morning around 3am and I was standing on my front porch having a smoke, when I heard a noise,it sounded like a squirrel or a really fast wild pig, when I looked that was not what I saw. I saw I large alien standing along the tree line it was white, very white all over, it had to stand at least 9 foot tall, its front legs were long at least 8 foot long not including its head and almost looked like elephant legs but slightly skinnier its torso and abdomen was a slightly flattened funnel shape leading down to it's rear legs that were only about 2 or 3 feet long. Its head was also kind of a funnel shape but more of an angled cylinder with a jagged bottom with no eyes that could be seen, it was fast moving along the edge of the woods and then appearing to look around almost like it was lost then at a right angle darted directly into the woods, 5 minutes later after hearing odd noises coming from the woods a large dimly glowing object shot straight up from about where! I saw the creature dart into the woods and the object eventually just disappeared from sight. The next day tracks of the creature were found and so was what looked like a landing site

Saw multiple(15) lights following eachother on the same trajectory.  Two more came from different directions and one huge light stayed 
 
Last night I was in my yard with my boyfriend having a smoke, when I saw lights moving through the sky. They seemed evenly spaced apart  following each other. They disappeared  behind a tree and didn't seem to come out the other side. We counted about 15 of them. Right after the last one past on the same trajectory another one came from a different direction and seemed to follow. Seconds later, a second light came from another direction and disappeared in the same direction but different trajectory. We were freaked so we looked out our front window and saw a REALY big light. It might have been a star because its movement was really slow but it gave me pause because it looked close and bright. Way bigger and closer then the string of lights and the two that followed. I didn't have my camera in my yard but I did briefly film the big light. It is noticeably different then the stars, as no other star showed up on camera.

Yellow orange lights moving in the sky of Connecticut USA 
 
On Friday 10 of April 2020 at 9:00 pm I returned home from work.  I park my car and look at the stars and the sky was very clear but the color of the stars was orange and started to move.  As I kept looking there were more orange lights moving in line.  Other in circles.  It was very impressive.  I called my wife and told her to look at the sky and she saw the same thing.  What an experience..

During the process of putting things away in my new upstairs apartment I looked out my window and I saw a 10' tall object suddenly appear about 100 feet from my window.  When it stopped it made very fast pendulum type movements.  It looked like a 4'in diameter multi-colored ball with a 6' multi-colored stick coming up from the center of it.  In 3 seconds it flung out upward, and disappeared into outer space.  I never heard a sound.

Black Delta Wing Aircraft flying low over Chicago 
 
Report two delta wing black low flying aircraft flying over the Bronzeville area of Chicago, IL flying south to north on Dec. 26, 2019 around 6:30 PM.

We were looking for the aurora borealis related to the recent G3 solar flares. Didn’t see that, but did see a linear white light about 3 finger widths just below the handle of the Big Dipper. It seemed to be moving slowly in a SW direction for several minutes and then it slowly faded away. We had a clear view of the sky with no obstructions(wires, etc). This is a very rural area. There was no cloud cover. We did not hear any engine or other noise. 
 
NUFORC: Starlink

Noticed an orb to the right of the moob 
 
Went outside to walk the dog and noticed a bright white orb toward the west to the right of the moon. I then walked east to walk my dog and then when I walked home I looked up and got nervous cause it seemed to come closer to me. I then put the dog I. The house and grabbed my phone. I went outside and did a full zoom and started recording video. It was moving around like a ping pong ball on the camera and it was blurry around the sides. At one point I lost it and pointed the camera down and then back up and the object grew in size and became translucent. I then zoomed back and it was a different distance away and it was changing shape into an an amoeba and it was ping pinging around. I then stopped the video and saw a blue fire field around where the object was. I grab inside and grabbed my wife outside and she couldn’t see the orb with her eyes and it was still clearly visible to me. However she could still see it in on the video. I will attach that video as well. Please note that if you view these videos on the iPhone you can zoom in further. At theend of the first video you can hear what sound Las like military jets though there is no visual on them in the video. Lastly i haven’t seen an orb like this since march and it was east over the park. I have no video but I have a picture. Please let me know if you have any questions.

Sighted orange glowing sphere slowly float through night sky then slowly fade into nothing. 
 
It's April 5th 2020 at approximately 9:50 p.m. I step outside I look up at the night sky at first glance I think I see a helicopter. At closer inspection I noticed that it was a orange glowing sphere that was floating across the night sky very slowly. I quickly run in to grab my phone to record it. Aware that the craft might have its sights on me I quickly flip the light switch on and off for Enough time to see where my phone was. I grabbed my phone run back outside the very second I pointed my phone at the craft. The craft slowly began to fade into nothing. If there are aliens Among Us right now it would make sense for them to observe us right now because everybody is inside not looking up.

White cluster of 20+ rotating objects in the sky forming a circle 
 
I was driving north on Delaware Avenue in Ankeny, IA when something caught my eye.  I looked up and saw what I first thought was a flock of white birds, like seagulls, very high in the sky.  I watched them for a while noticing there were probably 20-30 in a circular formation.  I realized they were not moving anywhere, but could see that each “bird” seemed to be rotating slowly.  I started wondering if they were white parachutes or Chinese lanterns.  They reminded me of a cluster of jelly fish just floating.  I pulled into my driveway and stood watching this for about 30 more seconds.  I grabbed my phone to take a video as I could not figure out what this was.  I tried taking a 10 second video, but it was so bright I couldn’t tell if I captured anything.  When I turned off the video, I looked up again and noticed the entire cluster had suddenly and quickly moved a significant distance away further north and it was harder to see them.  Suddenly they were all ! in a vertical formation (a very straight line) one above the other, and they shot straight upwards very fast and disappeared into the sky.  There were not any clouds, but they seemed to disappear like they had gone into a cloud bank.  When I looked at the video I took, there is nothing there but sky.  I literally gasped when they were suddenly in the vertical line and shot straight up and disappeared.  I get goose bumps every time I recall this event.

Cigar shaped UFO captured flying above Garden of the Gods with an aircraft to the east ,possibly investigating 
 
I was going through some pictures that I took from a summer vacation trip through the Garden of the Gods in Colorado Springs, CO, in late July, 2019 and I noticed a cigar shaped figure in the photo and another aircraft.  One aircraft looks like a fighter jet (Air force Academy in Colorado Springs).

Multiple unexplained moving objects above CDA 
 
Went outside to take a night photo of my yard with iPhone 11 and a tripod.  Hear a very loud HC coming from a distance and looked up to see it pass low over the tree-line.  That is when I saw two additional objects bright white, quite a ways up in the night sky.  I did not think to much of them, as I figured they were satellites, but they started to move erratically. I noticed another 4-5 in the sky.  Some had to be closer, while others further away, as they were less bright and smaller in size.  What struck we was the flight patterns, it was illogical what these objects were doing.  They would go slowly one direction, stop (or almost) and then loop around the other direction, as if it was me playing with a laser pointer in the sky. My iPhone allows me to take night photos. I was able to capture a scene with two of the objects streaking on a 5 second night shutter count. Somehow (before trying the intended attempt) while taking one of my iPhone pics of my yard, wh! ile reviewing the picture, I noticed this long white streak in the background of that photo. This photo was using a 25 second night mode shot, on a tripod. I have never seen objects like these ones before ... whatever they were.

6 came in view one then another, straight path S/E to N/W red/yellow glow, at a distance they at times seem to disappear and return. 
 
I was going to check my mailbox, at 20:35 or so I turned to call my dog and observed an odd light in the sky (initially one light). The objects were triangular (appearing like an upright Conquistador Hat). They were lit up like a glow (not lights like a conventional aircraft). They silently moved from southeast to northwest direction. They were lit in a red/yellow color but seem to have a dark metallic boarder at the lower base. There were a total of 6 that came into view one at a time approximately 2 minutes apart on the same path, very silent, not a sound. Once they got miles pass, they seem to elevate and vanish (two of them vanished overhead and returned then disappeared miles away). I called a neighbor to come out and see them, they saw them as well. I videoed a few of them, then (and I don’t care who believes it) the video recording stopped and the video option on my iPhone was gone (all other options were available). After the last craft went over I waited for any others then got my mail, went in the house turned the camera back on my iPhone and the video option was back available. About 15 minutes later I went outside and there were helicopters to my Northwestern sky. I am a retired Army Senior Non-Commissioned Officer.

Fast moving soundless white sphere 
 
A small white spherical object moved across the sky from NW to SE in a straight trajectory from horizon to horizon with seconds and was quite visible in the clear daytime sky.  A plane was flying far above in the sky at the time and appeared to be moving very slowly in comparison.  In comparison the plane appeared larger.  There was no sound and it left no trail.  I've never seen anything like it before and wondered if satellites can be seen during the daytime like that and if they move across the sky that quickly?  (Although it appeared to me to be closer to the Earth than the plane far above it, but maybe that was an illusion to my eye?)

Observed two glimmering craft over Powell River that faded and disappeared as a Coast Guard or military aircraft approached. 
 
I was on a sailboat by myself travelling from Sturt Bay to the Powell River government dock in the morning.  At approxiamtely 11:00 hours while I was just off Grief Point I noticed two very bright lights about 500-800 feet above the pulp mill/dam.  I took my sunglasses off to try and focus, they were glimmering bright like the sun shining on stainless steel and appeared circular disk shaped with a raised portion in the middle maybe equalling about half the total diameter, I can only guess at this because the brightness was different in the middle. 
 
The objects were also large, probably over 50 feet in diameter and their distance apart appeared equal to their distance above the ground. 
 
As I observed, I also saw what I believed was a local Coast Guard (large red aircraft) surveillance rescue aircraft coming from the south hearing directly towards the craft at a slightly higher elevation.  It appeared to fly between the objects. 
 
As the aircraft came closed the objects didn't move, it appeared they faded, the glimmering became less and less to dim shapes and then nothing, just the blue sky and cloud behind.  It almost looked like they became cloaked with the background sky. 
 
Please note, the sun was behind me as I was travelling, possibly accounting for the glimmering on the craft, also I was not looking directly at or at and angle into the sun.  I don't know what I saw, but don't think it was a trick of my eyes and the sun. 
 
Trying to contact me might be difficult as I am up the coast on my boat, poor cell service and limited access to computers.  Who knows what it was…sun dogs??   
 
Take care ((name deleted))
